attributes.NAME: Abdul Latif Jameel Building
attributes.DESCR: Housing the students studying Business, Accounting, Economics, the Abdullatif Jameel Building is one of the most important buildings at AUC since it is a building that is a building. Building, building, building. Some text here. Building.

attributes.NAME: Americana Food Court
attributes.DESCR: The Americana Food Court is a social foodie hub in the middle east that focuses on delivering the highest-quality, most delicious food on the planet.

attributes.NAME: AUC Pool
attributes.DESCR: The pool is where people can swim, have a good time, maybe play some water polo. It's a great place to get a serious refresh in the summer, and while it can be cold in the winter, it still can be okay if it's heated. Is it heated? Find out on the next episode of "Who knows!?"
